            {
              "text": "During this segment, the USVI - P.R. Friendship Day Queen is seen waving the flags of the USVI, P.R., and the USA. In what ways does this performance embody coloniality? How can solidarity help us look beyond the mediating force of the imperial center (continental U.S.)? "
